Lisbon, London, Madrid, Milan, Moscow, Oslo, Paris, Sofia, Stockholm, Vienna, Vilnius, Warsaw, Zurich</li><li><strong>Asia: </strong>Bursa, Dubai, Hong Kong, Singapore, Tokyo</li><li><strong>Oceania: </strong>Sydney</li><li><strong>Africa: </strong>Johannesburg</li></ul><p>Wow!&nbsp; Pretty good chance you or your customers live near one of those locations.</p><p>They\u2019re a bit new \u2013 their WHMCS still has some placeholder text and their site is still coming together.&nbsp; But I love the ambition.&nbsp; They also offer VPN and high-bandwidth plans.</p><p>You\u2019ll need to contact them if you want Looking Glass or test IP information.&nbsp; <a href=\"https://acroservers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AcroServers</a> is a Polish company (NIP: 6871971968) with public WHOIS.&nbsp; You can read their <a href=\"http://acroservers.com/download/Regulamin-sklepu-internetowego-AcroServers.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">terms of service</a> on their web site\u2026if you speak Polish.&nbsp; Hopefully they\u2019ll get it translated to other languages soon.&nbsp; They accept Paypal and BitCoin. &nbsp;You can find test IP information <a href=\"https://acroservers.com/locations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">on their site</a>.</p><p><strong>Here\u2019s what they had to say:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cWe offer instant activated VPS Cloud worldwide, 1Gbit/s (37 locations), 2Gbit/s (20TB bandwitch) and VPN services. Starting from 5EUR with already 1Gb/s. Our goal is to provide secured VMs and our policy is all about your privacy.\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Here are the offers:</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>VPS 1</b></p><ul><li><div>1 CPU</div><div></div></li><li><div>512 MB RAM</div><div></div></li><li><div>10 GB SSD</div><div></div></li><li><div>1 Gbps (shared)</div><div></div></li><li><div>500 GB transfer</div><div></div></li><li><div>5.00EUR/month</div><div></div></li><li><div>Cloud/KVM</div><div></div></li><li><div>Coupon: lowendtalk</div></li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">[</span><a style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\" href=\"https://cp.acroservers.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER</a><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">]</span></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>VPS 2</strong></p><ul><li><div>1 CPU</div><div></div></li><li><div>1GB RAM</div><div></div></li><li><div>30 GB SSD</div><div></div></li><li><div>1 Gbps (shared)</div><div></div></li><li><div>1.5TB transfer</div><div></div></li><li><div>10.00EUR/month</div><div></div></li><li><div>Cloud/KVM</div><div></div></li><li><div>Coupon: lowendtalk</div></li><li>[<a href=\"https://cp.acroservers.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></td><td valign=\"top\">&nbsp;<p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table><div></div><div>Really hoping the community gives these guys a checkout and lets us known below how they do.&nbsp; Thank you!</div><div></div><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Facroservers-offering-service-in-nearly-every-city-in-the-world-from-e5-mo-1gbps-kvm%2F&amp;t=AcroServers%3A%20Offering%20Service%20in%20%28Nearly%29%20Every%20City%20in%20the%20World%20%28from%20%E2%82%AC5%2FMo%2C%201Gbps%20KVM%29\